title: First Week of November 20th Options Trading For Fiat Chrysler Automobiles
content:
at 11:35 AM EDT Investors in Fiat Chrysler Automobiles NV (FCAU) saw new options become available this week, for the November 20th expiration. At Stock Options Channel, our YieldBoost formula has looked up and down the FCAU options chain for the new November 20th contracts and identified one put and one call contract of particular interest.
